        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 15 at 7:11AM MDT until June 15 at 7:45AM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>At 711 AM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Cohagen, or 19
miles southeast of Jordan, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Cohagen, Steve Fork, Jordan, and Edwards.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.

Torrential rainfall is occurring with this storm, which may produce
ponding on area roadways.</instruction>
